<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <title>Landing Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="vendors/css/vendor.bundle.base.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/vertical-layout-light/style.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="images/favicon.png" />
    <style>
        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)), url('images/1.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
        }

        .logo-container {
            position: absolute;
            top: 30px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }

        .logo-container img {
            max-width: 80px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .button-group {
            padding-top: 3%;
        }

        .button-group a {
            min-width: 135px;
            padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            margin-right: 1rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button-group a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #212529;
            text-align: center;
            vertical-align: middle;
            user-select: none;
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            line-height: 1.5;
            border-radius: 0.25rem;
            transition: color 0.15s ease-in-out, background-color 0.15s ease-in-out, border-color 0.15s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.15s ease-in-out;
        }

        .btn:not(:disabled):not(.disabled) {
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-landingpage {
            background-color: #0F8EC8;
            background-image: none;
            border-color: #ffffff;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-landingpage:not(.btn-inverse-light) {
            color: #D7F2FF;
        }

        .btn-landingpage:hover {
            background-color: #0F8EC8;
            color: #D7F2FF;
            border-color: #D7F2FF;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-landingpage.focus,
        .btn-landingpage:focus {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(15, 142, 200, 0.5);
        }

        .btn-landingpage.disabled,
        .btn-landingpage:disabled {
            color: #0F8EC8;
            background-color: transparent;
        }

        .btn-landingpage.active,
        .btn-landingpage:active,
        .show>.btn-landingpage.dropdown-toggle {
            color: #20b4f8;
            background-color: #D7F2FF;
            border-color: #D7F2FF;
        }

        .nowrap-title {
            color: #20b4f8;
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            h4 {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            
            .button-group {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                padding-top: 5%;
            }

            .button-group a {
                min-width: 150px;
                padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
                margin-right: 0;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <section class="hero-section text-center d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
        <div class="logo-container">
            <img src="images/Logo Perpustakaan Medayu.webp" alt="Logo Perpustakaan Medayu">
        </div>
        
        <div class="container">
            <h1><b>Satu Aplikasi untuk<br><span class="nowrap-title">Presensi & Laporan Harian</span></b></h1>
            <h4>Catat presensi dan kirim laporan harian langsung dari perangkat Anda, tepat waktu dan terintegrasi.</h4>
            <div class="button-group">
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-landingpage">Login</a>
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-landingpage">Register</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>

</html>